'''Amr Arafa''' (yavutse 9 Ukuboza 1962), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Egiputa . <ref>https://egyptindependent.com/director-amr-arafa-concludes-shooting-men-30-sana-moqattam-scenes/</ref> Ufatwa nk'umwe mu bakora amafilime meza muri sinema yo mu Misiri, Arafa azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filime zatsindiye ibihembo bya ''Africano'', ''Zahaymar'', ''Helm Aziz'' na ''Akher Deek Fi Masr'' . <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/person/1049257/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 9 Ukuboza 1962 i Cairo, mu Misiri . Se Saad Arafa nawe yari umukinnyi wa firime cyane. Saad yavutse ku ya 1 Mata 1923, apfa ku ya 1 Nyakanga 1998. Yakoze firime nyinshi zizwi mu gisekuru cye nka ''Al E'iteraf'', ''Marzooka'' na ''Demoua 'Fi Lailat El Zefaf'' . <ref>http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/5/35/359176/Arts--Culture/Stage--Street/Late-Egyptian-filmmaker-Saad-Arafa-honoured-on-th-.aspx</ref>

Mukuru wa Amr, Sherif Arafa nawe ni umukinnyi wa firime uzwi cyane mu Misiri. Yavutse ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1960. Muri firime ze zizwi cyane harimo, ''Birds of Darkness'', ''Mafia'', ''Halim'' na ''Welad El Am'' .

Mu 2005, Arafa yimukiye muri [[Amerika]] kugira ngo arangize amashuri. Hanyuma yamaze igihe kinini muri [[Amerika]] imyaka 11 mumashuri yigihe gito. Yashinze kandi isosiyete ye bwite ishinzwe imicungire y’ubucuruzi, nyuma yizeza ikarita y’icyatsi mu 2015. <ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/inspired-life/wp/2016/08/25/this-man-launched-a-website-so-people-can-invite-refugees-to-stay-in-their-homes/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wa sinema mu 1983 akurikiza inzira ya se. Mu 1991, Amr yashinze uruganda rwe bwite, FinalCut Film Production. Kuva icyo gihe, yakoze kandi ayobora firime nyinshi, iyamamaza, serivise za televiziyo na documentaire. <ref name="vimeo">https://vimeo.com/amrarafa</ref>

Mu 2001, yayoboye kandi atunganya filime ye ya mbere ya ''Africano'' . Iyi filime yafatiwe muri Afurika y'Epfo kandi yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2001 mu Misiri. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nyuma ikerekanwa mu bihugu bya Afurika byegeranye ndetse no mu [[Burayi]]. Muri Koweti, iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 31 Ukwakira 2001 mu gihe mu Bugereki, yasohotse muri Archive Film Archive ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2012. <ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0290402/</ref><ref>http://english.alarabiya.net/en/media/television-and-radio/2014/07/12/Saraya-Abdeen.html</ref>

Nyuma yo gutsinda filime yumukobwa, yakomeje gukora umwuga wo kuyobora neza muri firime: ''Akher Deek Fi Masr'' (2017), ''Men 30 Sana'' (2016), Urukurikirane rwa TV ''Saraya Abdeen'' (2015), ''Abu El Nil'' (2013), ''Helm Aziz'' ( 2011), ''Zahaymar'' (2010), ''Ibin el-Qunsul'' (2009), ''El Shabah'' (2008), ''Gaaltany Mogreman'' (2006) na ''El Sefara Fel Emara'' (2004). <ref name="vimeo">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://vimeo.com/amrarafa "Amr Arafa films"]. vimeo<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">4 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref><ref>https://www.elcinema.com/en/work/wk1872179/review/</ref>

